01:59:18.780 --> 01:59:21.780
Oh, well, we knew it was the other time. It was never-

01:59:21.780 --> 01:59:24.780
They were surprised. But our existence, we weren't surprised about this.

01:59:24.780 --> 01:59:29.780
But my mother used to have relative come to visit me, because I had a root, so-

01:59:29.780 --> 01:59:31.780
It was white.

01:59:31.780 --> 01:59:33.780
Yeah, so there's no deal.

01:59:33.780 --> 01:59:40.780
And my sister, Joseph, now probably only identified with black Latiners in the country.

01:59:40.780 --> 01:59:44.780
Those who claim color.

01:59:44.780 --> 01:59:48.780
So the resistance comes on the white side.

01:59:48.780 --> 01:59:51.780
I mean, the white-well-

